What is RPG MAKER 2003?
RPG MAKER 2003 is a software application that allows the user to create their own role-playing game. Its uses can also extend into creation of games of other genres, visual presentations and educational tools. RPG MAKER 2003 is distributed with a set of resources named the Run-Time Package (or "RTP"). Please make sure to install the RTP read the RTP EULA before using this product.

For any inquiries, technical problems or other support, please contact us:
support@rpgmakerweb.com

