What is RPG MAKER 2003 Runtime Package?
RPG MAKER 2003 Runtime Package (RTP) is a collection of materials containing graphic, music and dll files which you can use when creating your own games with RPG MAKER 2003. Please install this RTP before installing and using RPG MAKER 2003. Using this RTP, you can reduce the total size of your game files created with RPG MAKER 2003. Users who wish to play games created with RPG MAKER 2003 are encouraged to install this RTP for convenience and smaller project download sizes.

